    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an alpha demo for High Times. It features the first 7 in-game days and is roughly about 3% of the full game. In this version, you will meet 8 characters (out of 20+), 5 of whom are the main characters (your exes). The main scenes in the game are fully voiced. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several features are not yet implemented, everything is work-in-progress, and things may change in the full version. If you encounter any game breaking problems or bugs, please let us know in the forums. Thank you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where one can <i>literally</i> eat their feelings, you work at The Hotbox, a special donut shop where the donuts you make are infused with mood enhancers — a substance that changes the emotions of your customers. From flavors that'll give them more courage, to ones that cheer them up, it's up to you to figure out which mood is best suited to help your troubled customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/33137a83a45c5edd072edcbb76da210e.avif?t=1727156400\" width=642 height=268 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If that's not enough, your exes are back in town, and they all have a bone to pick with you. Too bad &quot;closure&quot; isn't one of the moods that's on the menu, so you'll have to navigate complex emotions through the power of heartfelt conversations, and perhaps, with the help of a donut or two.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy donuts, listening to stories, and mending relationships, then get ready for the High Times! 🍩</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/e9082d07283d1940a5a1974ca3039b1e.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>A Sweet Kind of Therapy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a mood confectioner, you have a variety of flavors in your arsenal, each corresponding to a different emotion — patience, sincerity, nostalgia, among others. What your customers say and feel changes depending on what you serve them, so be careful; it's not just about serving donuts, you're also serving advice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/cb95f4a7afbc4861e00cface75555bc2.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/cb95f4a7afbc4861e00cface75555bc2.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/cb95f4a7afbc4861e00cface75555bc2.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Be the Best Donut Joint in Town</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be your own boss and manage a café, prepare and design donuts from scratch, serve the right orders to make customers happy, collect tips, unlock new tools and ingredients, upgrade your shop, and discover recipes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/07550b06d46bb0c00f4b3e0bfc9cf64f.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Closure SImulator</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've dated them, ghosted them, and now they're back with a vengeance. Your exes are now your customers, giving you the chance to finally say all the unsaid things that have been lingering. Will you heal from the trauma of the past, and perhaps even experience the most elusive and mythical of all emotions—closure?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/def8dbb19f3d2c41e921e4ece7d2ada2.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>English Voice Acting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A star-studded cast of professional English voice actors will be bringing the cast to life! Every character will be voiced, except the player's.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/d152cda3497170e01666ac7ef126bd02.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/d152cda3497170e01666ac7ef126bd02.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/d152cda3497170e01666ac7ef126bd02.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Choices Matter &amp; Multiple Endings</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The donuts you serve and the choices you make in the story ultimately affect your relationships. Customers will remember what you say to them, so think twice before making that decision! Will you remain as friends, or rekindle an old romance? The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/abaebd9805c2afa162e1a5e3733fa4f3.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>A Cast of Misfits</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aside from your exes, the town of San Mazo is full of zany misfits. From a mommy lover to a girl in a chicken suit, get to know them all, serve their favorite donuts, and find out what makes them tick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/514f2164a4f0fde9c5eecda3cb412d93.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Customizable Main Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the face that broke a lot of hearts for a more personal experience. Players can opt for a male or female character, and have the freedom to customize their appearance like skin color, hairstyle, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/150707458dfb5114b62d2acd17f6b32b.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/150707458dfb5114b62d2acd17f6b32b.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/150707458dfb5114b62d2acd17f6b32b.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Dynamic Comic Book-Styled Visuals</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the story come to life with over 50+ animated comic book-styled panels and vibrant illustrations (CGs)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.poster.avif?t=1727156400\" width=630 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.webm?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221840/extras/02078962a2ca8ef9838af307d3411d6f.mp4?t=1727156400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🍩 <strong>Original Soundtrack</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibe during service time to a blend of originally composed grunge and lo-fi soundtracks.</p>",
